column3:
The Last Dregs is looking to resolve a fishy situation.

※Please note that the difficulty of this quest has been synced to your current level. Furthermore, you may not proceed with a class or job that is different from when you accepted this quest.
Deliver the requested materials to the all-purpose service unit.

<If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),16))><If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),IntegerParameter(2)))>Mine <SheetEn(Item,3,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> from the Elysian seas.<Else/>Deliver <SheetEn(Item,2,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> to the all-purpose service unit.</If><Else/><If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),17))><If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),IntegerParameter(2)))>Gather <SheetEn(Item,3,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> from the Elysian seas.<Else/>Deliver <SheetEn(Item,2,IntegerParameter(5),2,1)/> to the all-purpose service unit.</If><Else/><If(Equal(IntegerParameter(4),18))><If(LessThan(IntegerParameter(1),IntegerParameter(2)))>Catch <SheetEn(Item,1,IntegerParameter(5),1,1)/> from the Elysian seas.<Else/>Deliver <SheetEn(Item,2,IntegerParameter(5),1,1)/> to the all-purpose service unit.</If><Else/></If></If></If>

The café is currently experiencing difficulties regarding fish-based foodstuffs. Methods of acquisition remain suboptimal and capable personnel shortages persist. To this end, staff has initiated a cultivation protocol to secure piscatory supply lines.
Testing of various feeds for aquaculture are presently underway. Your assistance is required to seek out additional materials.
When you are prepared, please provide bryophyte samples from the Elysian seas to the all-purpose service unit.
When you are prepared, please provide seaweed samples from the Elysian seas to the all-purpose service unit.

When you are prepared, please provide stickleback samples from the Elysian seas to the all-purpose service unit. Purchase of gold salmon roe from unit
N-0598 is strongly advised.
Scanning inventory... <whirr> No aquaculture feed samples detected. Awaiting delivery of acceptable samples.
Scanning inventory... <whirr> Potential aquaculture feed samples detected. Please insert samples to continue.
Scanning samples... Nutritional levels acceptable. Please report to Stigma-4 for compensation.
Report from the all-purpose service unit received. Your contributions are greatly appreciated.

Extrapolating outcomes based on success of cultivation protocol... Should the café become reliably and adequately stocked with fish-based foodstuffs, Grebuloffs are predicted to experience the highest growth in satisfaction levels.
Aquaculture testing will resume shortly. Please stand by and await further instructions.
